    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended primarily for those looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine currently has significant trouble idling and requires a comprehensive mechanical overhaul to be roadworthy again. The transmission is slipping, and there are visible signs of wear including heavy rust on the undercarriage and a worn-out interior. While it is not currently suitable for daily driving, it holds value for someone with the tools and time to restore it.",
